              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "GELI"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                "  80 cm3 Ge(Li) detector (resolution 2.1 keV at",
                "1332 keV, efficiency 16.5% relative to a 3\" x 3\"",
                "NaI crystal at a distance of 25 cm)."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Each stack consisted of a number of high purity target",
                "foils (Co,V or Ti), alternately followed by a high",
                "purity 25 um Al catcher foil and by commercial grade",
                "Al degrader foils.",
                " The efficiency of the detector was determined using",
                "calibrated gamma-sources of 22Na, 54Mn, 57Co, 60Co,",
                "137Cs, 133Ba, 226Ra and 241Am."
              ]
            }
          ],
